title: Pretty Girls - Britney Spears & Iggy Azalea
description:
"Pretty Girls" is a song recorded by American singer Britney Spears and Australian rapper Iggy Azalea. It was released on May 4, 2015, by RCA Records. The song was produced by the Anglo-American trio The Invisible Men, composed of Jason Pebworth, George Astasio and Jon Shave, who also contributed with songwriting credits along with Azalea, Maegan Cottone and the members of British girl group Little Mix.

The music video for "Pretty Girls" premiered on May 13.
